5</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λάκε δ᾽ ἀσπίς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:277\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.277</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λάκε δ᾽ ὀστέα</foreign> the bones <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cracked, broke with a crash</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:616\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.616</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λάκε δ᾽ ἀμφὶ πυρὶ ὕλη</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">crackled</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:694\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">694</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔλακον ἀξόνων βριθομένων χνόαι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">creaked</tr_> under the weight, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:153\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">153</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.):—this sense occurs only in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 2</tns> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram> </gramGrp> </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n62023.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of animals, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">scream</tr_>, of the falcon, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀξὺ λεληκώς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:141\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.141</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of the nightingale in the falcon's talons, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τί λέληκας</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:207\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">207</biblScope> </bibl>; also, of dogs, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">howl, bay</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Σκύλλη . . δεινὸν λελακυῖα</foreign> Od.l.c.; rare in Prose, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐ μινυρίζει οὐδὲ λέληκεν</foreign>, of the black eagle, Arist.l.c.:—this sense occurs only in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">pf.</tns>, exc. in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Med.\">Med.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κύνες λελάκοντο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:145\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">145</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n62023.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of human beings, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shout, scream, cry aloud</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λέληκεν ἢν καὶ μηδέν᾽ ἀνθρώπων ὁρᾷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0260.tlg001:7:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Se